                            <input type="radio" name="cat_small_children1" id="yes_small_children2" value="yes">Yes
                        </label>
                        <label for="no_small_children2">
                            <input type="radio" name="cat_small_children1" id="no_small_children2" value="no">No
                        </label>
                    </p>
    
                    <div class="comment-section">
                        <p>Additional information regarding your pet:</p>
                        <textarea name="cat_comment1" id="cat_comment" cols="5" rows="8" > </textarea>
                    </div>
    
                    <p>
                        <label for="name2">Your name (Provide your full name):
